::Kluster::

Kluster looks up at Menasor, watching him fly up. He aims and fires 
two missiles at the large bot's chest, not sure if his previous two 
missiles had hit.




--- In nbwrpg@y..., Robert Dahl <rdahl@s...> wrote:
> The claws of Iron Raptor barely scratched Menasor's heavy armor, 
and was to
> busy with Prowl to notice the small stinging sensation, until she 
bit into
> him. He wasnt thinking clearly, all he knew was that something was 
on him,
> and he had to get it off. His powerful legs buckled as he bent 
down, and
> then extended with him jumping high into the air, and starting to 
fly,
> hoping to make his attackers fall off with that. The metal surface 
that
> Iron Raptor tore into was starting to corode, her teeth where having
> problems penetrating the metal, but it was slowly melting away.
